caption.p: MTT colorimetric assay of cancer cell-cytotoxicity of synthesized FeNPs and SH essential oil on the MCF-7and K-562 human cancer cells at different concentrations. (a) MCF-7 cancer cell line, (b) K-562 cancer cell line. Each bar represents the mean ± SD (standard deviation) of three independent tests; ∗ ∗∗ represent statistical significance between control versus each MCF-7 and K-562 cancer cell lines at ∗ P < 0.01 considered significant and ∗∗ P < 0.001 highly significant levels using (ANOVA)/Tukey tests.
